Merge pull request #130 from AnderWeb/fileprovider

Use a local FileProvider when sending icons back to an app.

title: Use a local FileProvider when sending icons back to an app.
message:
Use a local FileProvider when sending icons back to an app.
This way Polar doesn't need to ask for Storage Permission just for sending a file to another app.

Ideally this method could be also used in other Polar areas, like aplying wallpapers or sending the icon requests.
